in '''anarchism''':
* [[Black Flag (newspaper)|''Black Flag'' (newspaper)]], a publication in Britain
* [[Chernoe Znamia|Chernoe Znamia (Чёрное знамя)]], an organisation in Russia
* An element of [[anarchist symbolism]]
